# NebulaForge 🚀

NebulaForge is a lightweight and scalable framework designed to accelerate the development of decentralized and AI-powered applications.

## Features

- Fast and modular architecture
- Secure API integration
- Easy deployment
- Open-source and community-driven

## Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/nebulaforge.git
cd nebulaforge
npm install
npm start

### فایل index.js

```javascript
class NebulaForge {
  constructor(name) {
    this.name = name;
  }

  initialize() {
    console.log(`🚀 ${this.name} initialized successfully.`);
  }

  getStatus() {
    return {
      project: this.name,
      status: "active",
      version: "1.0.0"
    };
  }
}

